Description:
    Generators for the TuberHub authorization system

Examples:
    rails generate hub:authorization:policy MODEL_NAME [--namespace=Namespace]
        Creates a new policy for the specified model with RBAC integration

    rails generate hub:authorization:controller NAMESPACE CONTROLLER_NAME [--actions=index,show,create,update,destroy] [--farm-scoped]
        Creates a new controller with the correct authorization setup

For complete documentation on the authorization system, including these generators,
please see the main documentation at docs/tuber_hub/AUTHORIZATION.md

